185
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,000
Erê erê erê...
 
Yes yes yes...

186
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,000
Wanoyê leçer o nîro...
 
Those Leçer ones today...

187
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:09,000
De... yirim (?) ez ketim çûkê xanê... her sal pirr in bûn...
 
So... I fell into the corner of the house... every year
