251
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,000
Mla gî bibîne.
 
Let everyone see.

252
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:51,000
Emê hejîr... hejîrê bînin... emê hejîra biçinin.
 
We will figs... bring figs... we will pick figs.

253
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:54,000
Dê...
 
So...

254
